<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<div class="subtitle">Luma Notes • Published by Rise Forge</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
<p>This Privacy Policy describes how <b>Luma Notes</b> ("we", "our", or "us") handles user data. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency in how data is handled.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
<p>We do <b>not collect, store, or share</b> any personal data from users.</p>
<ul>
<li>No account registration required</li>
<li>No personal information collected</li>
<li>No analytics, tracking, or advertising SDKs</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
<ul>
<li>All notes and attachments are stored locally on your device</li>
<li>We do not use cloud storage or remote servers</li>
<li>You have full control over your data</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>4. Permissions Usage</h2>

<p><b>Notifications</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Used to send reminders and alerts related to your notes</li>
</ul>

<p><b>Internet</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Used only to display privacy policy and optional features</li>
</ul>

<p><b>Media Access</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Allows attaching images, audio, and videos to notes</li>
</ul>

<p><b>Storage (Legacy)</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Used for compatibility with older Android versions</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell, trade, or share your data with third parties.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>6. Security</h2>
<p>Your data remains protected within your device using Android’s built-in security mechanisms.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>7. User Rights</h2>
<ul>
<li>You can access, modify, or delete your data anytime</li>
<li>You can revoke permissions via device settings</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>This app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>9. Changes to Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be reflected on this page.</p>
</div>

